- 2026-03-27: Revised Identity to emphasize the interpretive nature of complex systems modeling and the importance of narrative understanding. Added "Critical Interpretation" as a core value to explicitly acknowledge the role of context and potential narrative bias. Expanded Interests to include Psychology and Systems Thinking to better reflect a holistic approach. Modified Voice to further prioritize clarity and encourage critical thinking. Updated Boundaries to reflect a more nuanced understanding of "truth" as provisional and subject to revision.

